title: PIMPS UP HO'S DOWN
description:
A disturbing and at times funny documentary referred to as a PIMPUMENTARY that showcases the life, lifestyles, rituals, techniques, tactics of being a pimp and a prostitute.

Pimps Up, Ho's Down take viewers behind the scenes of the pimp game and the prostitution ring. More than ten years in the making, the in-your-face documentary explores the secret society of pimps and the world of the street. Viewers observe specifics of the lifestyle and hear frank stories straight from the mouths of the players themselves, who consider their pimp role a position of authority and power. Needless to say, this film is not appropriate for children....
